            <title>[SOLR-16906] Packaged Prometheus config ignores REPLICATION metrics</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/SOLR-16906</link>
                <project id="12310230" key="SOLR">Solr</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;The solr-exporter-config.xml provided with Solr does not pick up REPLICATION metrics. This is probably unintentional, as it has configuration for `REPLICATION.replication` metrics, however actual metric names starts with `REPLICATION./replication` (notice the slash).&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Related config introduced in &lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/SOLR-15572&quot; title=&quot;Improve the default Prometheus exporter config performance&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;SOLR-15572&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;SOLR-15572&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
